This repository contains the warm up task for the Google Summer of Code 2017 DBpedia Chatbot



A simple chatbot to translate arabic numbers into roman numbers. 

Usage

run the script: javac Main.java and then java Main and then type queries. Type 'stop' to exit.

Examples:

   Hello! I am a simple chatbot to translate arabic numbers into roman numbers.Ask me to translate arabic numbers or press 'stop' to exit.

Please write a arabic number to convert : 23
Arabic Number 23   converted in Roman number is : XXIII

Please write a arabic number to convert : 123
Arabic Number 123   converted in Roman number is : CXXIII

Please write a arabic number to convert : stop
See you ! bye ...




    

